 "Well," he said taking her with him as he walked towards the map. " We have 
two pred tribes here and a Maximal. Now the one pred is headed by Megatron. 
Not my old self a new one. The Maximal is leaded by Rodimus Prime. He I wish 
to save for last.  One of the pred factions will be our first target. While 
alling with the other...what do u think?"
